OL,7,FA man who was shot dead in the car
OL,8,Fpark of a Derby police station rushed
OL,9,Fa firearms officer in the moments
OL,10,Fbefore he was shot, an inquest into
OL,11,Fhis death has heard.
OL,13,FMarius Ciolac was shot by police in
OL,14,Fthe car park of Ascot Drive police
OL,15,Fstation in Derby on 7 October 2022.
OL,17,FThe inquest into his death started
OL,18,Ftoday (22 January) and is expected to
OL,19,Flast four weeks.
