OL,3,CDerby knifeman 'rushed firearms
OL,4,Cofficer' moments before he was shot by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FThe court heard Mr Ciolac walked into
OL,8,Fthe compound at the police station
OL,9,Farmed with a knife just before 10am.
OL,11,FCCTV, bodycam and mobile phone footage
OL,12,Fshowed Mr Ciolac banging on the door
OL,13,Fof the police station and a police car
OL,14,Fwindow.
OL,16,FThe inquest heard officers repeatedly
OL,17,Fshouted at him to put the knife down.
OL,18,FAt one point a taser gun was fired but
OL,19,Fhad no effect as he was wearing thick
OL,20,Fmotorbike trousers.
