OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FArmed officers then arrived. A police
OL,8,Fbaton gun was fired using a rubber
OL,9,Fbullet, along with stun grenades.
OL,11,FFootage then showed Mr Ciolac moving
OL,12,Fquickly towards one of the firearms
OL,13,Fofficers who then fired a single shot
OL,14,Fwhich hit him in the abdomen.
OL,16,FHe then fell to the ground, and
OL,17,Fseveral officers dropped on him,
OL,18,Fwrestled the knife from his hand and
OL,19,Fhandcuffed him.
