OL,7,FParamedics arrived just after 10am and
OL,8,Fshortly after Mr Ciolac suffered a
OL,9,Fcardiac arrest.
OL,11,FHe was taken to the Queen's Medical
OL,12,FCentre in Nottingham where he died at
OL,13,F11:25am.
