OL,7,FThe IOPC said in 2022 that three
OL,8,Fknives of various sizes were recovered
OL,9,Ffrom the scene, along with a cat in a
OL,10,Fbag.
OL,12,FDerbyshire Police said after the
OL,13,Fincident the cat was safe and was
OL,14,Ftaken into the care of a cat centre.
OL,16,FThe inquest continues, and is expected
OL,17,Fto run into February.
